message: Let's get this started! Take it or leave it?
Meet in the middle? I was thinking more like meet at the high end!
You're not getting off that easy! Take it or walk away!
50/50? You're not even trying to negotiate! I want more!
Last chance, Bob! Take this or I'll make you regret it!
I'm not giving up yet! One more try!
You think you're getting the upper hand? Think again, Bob! I'm not settling for that!
Fine, let's do it. But don't say I didn't warn you...
